caption:
Another successful sold out Golf Tourney under my belt. Yesterday was a dream come true. The @WashedLordGolf “Oceanside Scramble” was incredible! 🤩🙌🏾 The weather was perfect and the vibes were unmatched! The entire day was maybe my best golf day ever! Thank you to everyone who came and supported and has supported my golf journey & movement. I’ll see you in April for the 2nd annual WLI! (date and course TBA soon) ⛳️🏆💎🔥🏌🏽‍♂️
Thank you @arrowoodgolfcourse for hosting us, the track was PURE 💦
